snippet.textDisplay: The first girl= Arctic Fox dye isn’t that good quality. I also don’t think the person who tried to pre lift her hair knew how to do it correctly to sort out uneven parts. If she’d have used a combo of Guy Tang greens in the Demi’s with added tones, would have been what she wanted. But arctic fox has a very cheap plastic like basic formula. That’s also why there were blue ends, as the green pigments fell out, just not the right dye. Guy Tang Demi’s would have been the thing.
